         <div class="heading-block style-4 black-color text-center margin-bottom-10 width-100">
          <h4>WHO WE ARE</h4>
        </div>
        <hr class="color mb-20">
        <p class="text-justify fz-20">We are committed to providing our customers with the best skills available on the market for information management, cloud services and infrastructure, cyber security and software development.</p>
        <p class="text-justify fz-20">We were founded in 2003 by a group of dedicated technical professionals with the aim of becoming a leader on the Romanian market for services related to infrastructure, cyber security and software development. Our goal is to consult our clients by offering an extensive portfolio of top solutions, with the skills of a team of highly qualified specialists who ensure the delivery of professional services to high quality standards. </p>
        <p class="text-justify fz-20">The ongoing process of developing technical expertise, combined with the effort to increase efficiency, makes Smart Control a reliable partner for providing and delivering IT integration services for a portfolio of complex solutions covering the on-premise, cloud and blockchain space.</p>
      </div>
